{"tid":975432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：代表團訪問新疆　相信當地反恐經驗可供參考","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:28:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5162d98506e8286dba594a2aed4e04103749c3e9","tid":975432,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437263-20190109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437263-20190109.htm&d=4%2BvgcLjDEU85daVKvUDpCjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9a092ce0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437263-20190109.htm&h=97be3205\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437263-20190109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，政府跨部門反恐專責組代表團上月到訪新疆期間，沒有參觀當地的「職業技能培訓機構」。<br />\n<br />\n李家超說，新疆過往多次出現恐襲，但近年情況得以控制和改善，相信當地的反恐經驗，可以為香港完善反恐政策提供參考，又指當局會出訪不同地方，交流反恐經驗，不會偏聽或帶有偏見。"}]}